---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<section id="audit" class="hero split">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>AI changed SEO.<br />Rank Higher in <span class="gradient-text">Google & AI</span></h1>
      <p>Show up first on Google and AI search engines when customers need you most. Built for contractors and restoration companies to get more calls and secure more jobs effortlessly.</p>
      
      <p class="hero-subtitle-tagline">BOOST YOUR SEO WITH THE POWERFUL SOLUTIONS</p>
      <div class="solution-badges">
        <span class="badge-bubble badge-red">
          <svg class="badge-icon-inline" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M2 11a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5a1 1 0 01-1 1H3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-5zM8 7a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v9a1 1 0 01-1 1H9a1 1 0 01-1-1V7zM14 4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v12a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1V4z" />
          </svg>
          Real-Time Rank Tracking
        </span>
        <span class="badge-bubble badge-green">
          <svg class="badge-icon-inline" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          Rank #1 on Google Maps
        </span>
        <span class="badge-bubble badge-orange">
          <svg class="badge-icon-inline" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M 12 3 L 10.088 8.813 A 2 2 0 0 1 8.813 10.088 L 3 12 L 8.813 13.912 A 2 2 0 0 1 10.088 15.187 L 12 21 L 13.912 15.187 A 2 2 0 0 1 15.187 13.912 L 21 12 L 15.187 8.813 A 2 2 0 0 1 13.912 8.813 Z" />
          </svg>
          Rank on ChatGPT & AI
        </span>
        <span class="badge-bubble badge-purple">
          <svg class="badge-icon-inline" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 3a1 1 0 00-1.447-.894L8.763 6H5a3 3 0 000 6h.28l1.771 5.316A1 1 0 008 18h1a1 1 0 001-1v-4.382l6.553 3.276A1 1 0 0018 15V3z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          Google LSA & PPC Lead Gen
        </span>
      </div>

      <!-- Audit Card -->
      <div class="audit-card">
        <div class="audit-card-header">
          <svg class="audit-icon" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M9 3.5a5.5 5.5 0 100 11 5.5 5.5 0 000-11zM2 9a7 7 0 1112.452 4.391l3.328 3.329a.75.75 0 11-1.06 1.06l-3.329-3.328A7 7 0 012 9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <h3>See Where You Rank Free</h3>
        </div>
        <p>Fill the input to get an instant AI ranking report for your domain.</p>
        <div class="audit-form">
          <div class="input-wrapper">
            <svg class="input-icon" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-1.5 0a6.5 6.5 0 11-13 0 6.5 6.5 0 0113 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 2.5a.75.75 0 01.75.75v5.5a.75.75 0 01-1.5 0v-5.5a.75.75 0 01.75-.75z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <input type="text" placeholder="yoursite.com" />
          </div>
          <button class="btn btn-audit">Get my Free Audit</button>
        </div>
        <div class="audit-progress">
          <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill"></div></div>
          <span class="progress-text">Step 1 of 2</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-image-container">
      <img src="/hero-combined.png" alt="Local SEO Ranking Heatmap and AI Search ChatGPT Recommendation Dashboard" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
